# Tutorial: Getting Started - Step 5: ait switch
# Shows: Apply detected context to terminal

Output getting-started-03-switch.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Title
Type "# Step 5: Switch terminal to match context"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Run switch command
Type "ait switch"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Show what changed
Type "# Terminal profile updated!"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

# Show the profile
Type "ait profile show"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# List available profiles
Type "ait profile list"
Enter
Sleep 3s
